map <C-c> <leader>c<space>
map <C-k> <leader>cm
" close current tab
nmap <C-p> :tabclose<CR>`.
" edit
nmap <C-h> cit
" this way we can simulate a real backspace, useful for plugins
imap <C-h> <BS>
" delete key, useful with <c-h> in insert mode
